Roswell is an American science fiction television series developed , produced , and co-written by Jason Katims .
The series debuted on October 6 , 1999 on The WB and moved to UPN for the third season ; The last episode aired on May 14 , 2002 .
In the United Kingdom , the show aired as both Roswell High and Roswell .
The series is based on the Roswell High young adult book series , written by Melinda Metz and edited by Laura J. Burns , who became staff writers for the television series .